                        "content": "In preparation for cataract surgery, the nurse is to administer prescribed eye drops. The nurse reviews the primary health care provider's prescriptions, expecting which type of eye drops to be prescribed?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nA mydriatic medication produces mydriasis or dilation of the pupil. Mydriatic medications are used preoperatively in the client with a cataract. These medications act by dilating the pupils; they also constrict blood vessels. A miotic medication constricts the pupil. An osmotic diuretic may be used to decrease intraocular pressure. A thiazide diuretic is not likely to be prescribed for a client with a cataract.",
                        "id": "33fdee624fbc4e9a99ec578e21f947ba",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "c4f66789703d4acabf4da62dbafffc60",
                                "content": "Carbachol"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "445ac1295f19465c847d8e52db7d3134",
                                "content": "Atropine sulfate"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "3581d24c7bba497c82089bafa660f52b",
                                "content": "Pilocarpine nitrate"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5ae47cda89214bc6bd19176f6bfb7ed8",
                                "content": "Pilocarpine hydrochloride"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "c4f66789703d4acabf4da62dbafffc60",
